    "959310": {
      "title": "On differential graded categories",
      "abstract": "Differential graded categories enhance our understanding of triangulated categories ::: appearing in algebra and geometry. In this survey, we review their foundations and report on ::: recent work by Drinfeld, Dugger\ufffdShipley, Toen, Toen\ufffdVaquie, and others."
